When you use our Platform, whether our Website or our App,
        we collect and store your information (personal information) which is provided by you from time to time by explicitly seeking permissions from YOU to get the required information. Our primary goal in doing so is to provide you a safe, efficient, smooth and customized experience and services. This allows us to provide services and features that meets your needs, and to customize our Platform to make your experience safer and easier and to improve the services provided by us. More importantly, we collect personal information from you that we consider necessary for achieving the aforementioned purpose.
        \nIn general, you can browse the Website or App without telling us who you are or revealing any personal information about yourself. However, to create an account on the Website or App, you must provide us with certain basic information required to provide customized services. The information we collect from you, inter alia, including:
        \na. your full name;
        \nb. email;
        \nc. mailing address;
        \nd. postal code;
        \ne. family details;
        \ng. phone number;
        \nh. Permanent Account Number (PAN);
        \ni. Academic records and certificates.
        \nj. Aadhaar card
        \nk. face picture
        \nl. Driving License
        \nm. Voter ID
        \nWhere possible, we indicate the mandatory and the optional fields. You always have the option to not provide your personal information by choosing not to use a particular service or feature on the Platform.
        \nWe also collect other identifiable information (your payment card details and transaction histories on the Platform) from you when you set up a free account with us. While you can browse some sections of our Platform without being a registered member as mentioned above, certain activities (such as availing of loans from the third-party lenders on the Platform) requires registration and for you to provide the above details. The Platform shall clearly display the personal information it is collecting from you, and you have the option to not provide such personal information. However, this will limit the services provided to you on the Platform.

We access, store and use the information we collect from you to provide our Services, to research and develop new ones.
        \nWe use personal information to provide the services you request, to customize your user experience and to improve our services. To the extent we intent to use your personal information to market any product to you, we will provide you the ability to opt-out of such uses.
        \nWe use your personal information to:
        \na. resolve disputes;
        \nb. troubleshoot problems;
        \nc. help promote a safe service;
        \nd. analytical analysis;
        \ne. measure consumer interest and satisfaction in our products and services;
        \nf. inform you about online and offline offers, products, services, and updates;
        \ng. customize your experience;
        \nh. detect and protect us against suspicious or illegal activity, fraud and other criminal activity;
        \ni. enforce our terms and conditions;
        \nj. improvement of our services and as otherwise described to you at the time of collection.
        \nIn our efforts to continually improve our product and service offerings, we collect and
        analyze demographic and profile data about our users\' activity on our Website.

We use the information provided by You in the following ways:
        \na. to establish identity and verify the same;
        \nb. monitor, improve and administer our Website / Platform ;
        \nc. provide our service i.e. perform credit profiling for the purpose of facilitating loans to You.
        \nd. design and offer customized products and services offered by our third-party financial partners;
        \ne. analyse how the Website is used, diagnose service or technical problems and maintain security;
        \nf. send communications notifications, information regarding the products or services requested by You or process queries and applications that You have made on the Website;
        \ng. manage Our relationship with You and inform You about other products or services We think You might find of some use;
        \nh. conduct data analysis in order to improve the Services / Products provided to the User;
        \ni. use the User information in order to comply with country laws and regulations;
        \nj. to conduct KYC for our third-party lending partners based on the information shared by the User;
        \nk. use the User information in other ways permitted by law to enable You to take financial services from our lending partners.
        \nWe will use and retain Your information for such periods as necessary to provide You the Services on our Website, to comply with our legal obligations, to resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.
